channel.title: IP Change?
channel.description:
Hi, I've just noticed after some recent changes to my DNS that my server listing is pointing to an incorrect host.
Would it be possible to have [url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=unscape-online.com]unscape-online.com[/url] changed so the host is server.unscape-online.com?
The listing has been up since 2011 so it would be a shame to have to create a new one.
Thanks
